        String tail = sc.next();
        int n = tail.length();//桁数
        String[] tailsp = tail.split("");
        String zero= "0";
        String one ="1";
        int count=0;
        for(int i=0;i<n;i++){
            if(i%2==0&&tailsp[i].equals(zero)){
                count ++;
            }
            if(i%2==1&&tailsp[i].equals(one)){
                count ++;
            }
        }
        n -=count;
        if(count > n){
            System.out.print(n);
        }else{
            System.out.print(count);
        }
        
    }
    
}
